    • Plant

      public Plant()

    • Plant

      public Plant​(java.lang.String bloomColors, int hardinessMax, int hardinessMin, int heightMaxInches, int heightMinInches, java.lang.String plantBotanicalName, int spacingMax, int spacingMin, int spreadMax, int spreadMin, java.lang.String commonName, java.lang.String soilMoisturePreference, java.lang.String sunlightExposure, java.lang.String[] floweringMonths, java.lang.String[] wildlifeAttracted, java.lang.String[] otherAttributes, boolean deerResistant, java.lang.String foliageColor, java.lang.String growthRate, java.lang.String saltTolerance, java.lang.String[] seasonsOfInterest, java.lang.String[] phytoremediationElementsCleaned, enums.PlantType type)
      Constructor for Plant. Creates a plant and sets its characteristics, attributes, requirements, and the group of plants it belongs to in addition to additional info such as salt tolerance of the plant and the types of wildlife attracted by the plant.
      Parameters:
      bloomColors - the String of the plant's bloom colors
      hardinessMax - the plant's maximum hardiness
      hardinessMin - the plant's minimum hardiness
      heightMaxInches - the plant's maximum height in inches
      heightMinInches - the plant's minimum height in inches
      plantBotanicalName - the String of the plant's botanical name
      spacingMax - the plant's maximum spacing in inches
      spacingMin - the plant's minimum spacing in inches
      spreadMax - the plant's maximum spread in inches
      spreadMin - the plant's minimum spread in inches
      commonName - the String of the plant's common name
      soilMoisturePreference - the String containing the soil moisture preference of the plant
      sunlightExposure - the String containing the plant's recommended level of sunlight exposure
      floweringMonths - the array of Strings containing the plant's flowering months
      wildlifeAttracted - the array of Strings containing the types of wildlife attracted by the plant
      otherAttributes - the array of Strings containing extra attributes of the plant
      deerResistant - the boolean indicating whether or not the plant is deer resistant
      foliageColor - the String containing the plant's foliage color
      growthRate - the String containing the plant's growth rate
      saltTolerance - the String containing the plant's salt tolerance level
      seasonsOfInterest - the array of Strings containing the plant's seasons of interest
      phytoremediationElementsCleaned - the array of Strings containing the plant's elements cleaned
      type - the PlantType of the plant
